Invocation Name: eight key concepts
des:
Hong's Martial Arts School and Alexa can help you learn new Korean terminology for your upcoming belt testing. You can review the flash cards and then test your knowledge. At any point you can say "Alexa, review mode" to switch to review or say "Alexa, test mode" to start a test. You can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next card. At any point during the test, you can say "Alexa, what's my score" to get your current test score.
This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
